  <dashboards>
    <dashboard name='Business Recommendations' type='storyboard'>
      <layout-options>
        <title>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' italic='true'>Business Recommendations</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </title>
      </layout-options>
      <style>
        <style-rule element='story-point-caption'>
          <format attr='width' value='1085' />
        </style-rule>
      </style>
      <size maxheight='964' maxwidth='1416' minheight='964' minwidth='1416' sizing-mode='fixed' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='2' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='98340' id='1' param='vert' removable='false' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98870' x='565' y='830'>
            <zone h='4564' id='3' type-v2='title' w='98870' x='565' y='830' />
            <zone h='10477' id='4' is-fixed='true' paired-zone-id='5' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard-nav' w='98870' x='565' y='5394' />
            <zone h='83299' id='5' paired-zone-id='4' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard' w='98870' x='565' y='15871'>
              <flipboard active-id='1' nav-type='caption' show-nav-arrows='true'>
                <story-points>
                  <story-point caption='Business Recommendations: Key insights from the analysis suggest focusing on profitable products, improving regional performance, retaining valuable customers, and leveraging forecasted trends for future growth.&#10;' captured-sheet='' id='1' />
                </story-points>
              </flipboard>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='49066' id='6' story-point-id='1' type-v2='text' w='96850' x='2264' y='17324'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>BUSINESS RECOMMENDATIONS</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Focus on high-performing product categories and increase investment in products generating maximum revenue.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Improve profitability in low-performing regions through targeted marketing and pricing strategies.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Strengthen customer retention by focusing on top revenue-generating customers and loyalty initiatives.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Prioritize products identified in Pareto Analysis, as a small percentage of products contribute the majority of sales.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Use forecasting insights for better inventory planning, resource allocation, and future business decisions.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Conclusion:
The analysis indicates strong opportunities for growth through product optimization, customer retention, regional improvement, and data-driven decision making.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <simple-id uuid='{9C29E109-3982-4A5D-8A44-AC135FAE49B8}' />
    </dashboard>
